<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>XSS Demo - Security Learning Lab</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .navbar {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      padding: 15px 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }
    .navbar a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }
    .navbar a:hover {
      opacity: 0.8;
    }
    .container {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .search-container {
      background: white;
      padding: 50px 40px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      color: #999;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .warning {
      background: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffc107;
      border-left: 5px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #856404;
    }
    .search-box {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    input[type="text"] {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-right: none;
      border-radius: 8px 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 15px;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #f5576c;
    }
    button {
      padding: 12px 25px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(245, 87, 108, 0.4);
    }
    button:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    .results {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      min-height: 80px;
      border-left: 5px solid #f5576c;
    }
    .results h2 {
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .result-text {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      word-break: break-all;
    }
    .demo-section {
      background: #ffe7e7;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-left: 5px solid #f5576c;
    }
    .demo-section h3 {
      color: #d32f2f;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .demo-section p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .demo-section code {
      background: white;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      color: #d32f2f;
      display: block;
      margin: 8px 0;
      border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
      word-break: break-all;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .links {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .links a {
      color: #f5576c;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .links a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .info-box {
      background: #fce4ec;
      border-left: 5px solid #c2185b;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #880e4f;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .search-container {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      .search-box {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      input[type="text"] {
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      button {
        border-radius: 8px;
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="navbar">
    <a href="/">‚Üê Security Learning Lab</a>
    <div>
      <a href="/login" style="margin-right: 20px;">Login</a>
      <a href="/search">Search</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="search-container">
      <h1>‚ö° XSS (Cross-Site Scripting) Demo</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Halaman Search yang Vulnerable</p>

      <div class="warning">
        <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è WARNING:</strong> Halaman ini sengaja dibuat vulnerable untuk tujuan pembelajaran. Jangan coba di website real!
      </div>

      <form action="/search" method="GET" class="search-box">
        <input type="text" name="q" placeholder="Masukkan kata pencarian atau payload..." value="<%= searchQuery %>">
        <button type="submit">Cari</button>
      </form>

      <% if (searchQuery) { %>
        <div class="results">
          <h2>Hasil Pencarian:</h2>
          <div class="result-text">
            Anda mencari: <%= searchQuery %>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% } %>

      <div class="demo-section">
        <h3>üö® Cara Eksploitasi XSS:</h3>
        <p><strong>Pilih salah satu payload berikut dan masukkan di search box:</strong></p>

        <p><strong>1. JavaScript Alert:</strong></p>
        <code>&lt;script&gt;alert('XSS Vulnerability!')&lt;/script&gt;</code>

        <p><strong>2. Image Error Handler:</strong></p>
        <code>&lt;img src=x onerror="alert('XSS')"&gt;</code>

        <p><strong>3. SVG onload:</strong></p>
        <code>&lt;svg onload="alert('XSS')"&gt;</code>

        <p><strong>4. Langsung dari URL:</strong></p>
        <code>/search?q=&lt;script&gt;alert('XSS')&lt;/script&gt;</code>

        <div class="info-box">
          <strong>Penjelasan:</strong> Karena input tidak di-encode/escape, script akan dijalankan langsung di browser. Dalam serangan real, attacker bisa mencuri cookies, session tokens, atau melakukan aksi berbahaya lainnya.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="links">
        <a href="/login">‚Üê Ke SQL Injection Demo</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
